\begin_layout Standard
Not surprisingly, all the sectors are negatively impacted.
 In the energy sectors, the oil is naturally the most impacted activity
 but the over ones, especially the gas production sectors, benefit from
 a inter-energy substitution effect and observe an increase in their demand.
 
\end_layout

